name: Jane Doe
description: Jane Doe is perfectly named because this strain is a bit of a mystery girl, though her genetics most likely include some OG. This strain is well-balanced with effects that provide euphoria and relief without sleepiness. This Jane is anything but plain, with a crisp lemon aroma and big, trichome-covered flowers that make her a beauty.
attributes_title: Euphoric, Happy, Relaxed, Tingly, Sleepy, Pain, Depression, Stress, Insomnia, Nausea, Dry Mouth, Dry Eyes, Dizzy
